    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust! It drives like a dream and has been pampered since day one. If you're looking for perfection, you've found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
