    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This specimen is mechanically pristine, having undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity and long-term reliability. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a limited-slip differential for precise corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, with bushings and dampening rates performing at original tolerances. Finished in a flawless factory coat with a fully documented service history, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
