      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a premium ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the leather is supple with no creasing, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Always garage-kept and strictly hand-washed, this car has been treated as a collector\u2019s piece rather than a daily driver. It comes with a complete, documented service history, two sets of keys, and original manuals. It is mechanically flawless and drives as tight as the day it was built. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
