    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exemplary caliber, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom-quality condition, exhibiting an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory refinement. Meticulously inspected to ensure absolute mechanical integrity, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
