    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total stunner! This car has been my baby\u2014garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it honestly still has that brand-new feel. It drives like an absolute dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for something in truly pristine condition without any of the headaches, this is the one! I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
