    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, this unit has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a Vanos overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and dampers, maintaining its celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in a pristine coat with an immaculate interior, this collector-grade specimen offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
